Telephone Number For Information: 800-553-3014<p><p>Top-Rated Funds - LIST<p>For Worth's annual mutual-fund performance ratings, we screened 777 funds. Starting with statistics from Morningstar, we calculated three exclusive ratings: return against a benchmark, risk level, and predictability.<p>We then assigned each of the 777 funds an overall Worth rating that combined the return, risk, and predictor scores into a single ranking, from $ to $$$$$. (For a complete description of how we assigned ratings, see "Best Funds: How We Picked Them.")<p>Only the very best funds received a $$$$$ rating -- we gave that rating to the top 5 percent in each of the return, risk, and predictor categories. Then, we subjected each of the $$$$$-rated funds to a final examination to come up with our choices for the top five funds (see "Best Funds: Best Of The Best - LIST").<p>Due to the constraints of our online format, we aren't able to include the complete list of 777 funds we examined. Instead, below is a list of top-ranked funds: the 47 funds that received $$$$$ ratings. For the complete fund list, along with statistical data on all 777 funds, pick up a copy of Worth's November issue at a newsstand.<p><p>WORTH'S $$$$$-RATED FUNDS
