<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT14-B11-154</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA032-000667-B011-47</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.worth.com:80/articles/Z9403E03.html 204.141.48.165 19970209141413 text/html 11346
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 14:15:00 GMT
