  <head>
    <title>PBHG &amp; switching techniques</title>
  </head>
  <body background="/imgs/goldbarsmooth.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#FF0000" vlink="#BB0000">
<table cellpadding=10 cellspacing=5 width=550>
<tr>
	<td width=390>
 <a href=/cgi/ad-relay.cgi?http://www.pcfn.com/6015.html?worth+PCFN16.gif+Message%20Boards>
